## ğŸ‘¨â€ğŸ’» API Endpoints  

### **User Management**  
- `POST /api/v1/user` â€“ Create a new user  
- `GET /api/v1/userbyid/:id` â€“ Fetch user by ID  
- `POST /api/v1/logout` â€“ Logout user  

### **Projects Management**  
- `GET /api/v1/projects` â€“ Fetch all projects  
- `POST /api/v1/projects` â€“ Add a new project  
- `GET /api/v1/projects/:id` â€“ Fetch project details  
- `PUT /api/v1/projects/:id` â€“ Update project  

### **Leave Management**  
- `GET /api/v1/leaves` â€“ Fetch leave requests  
- `POST /api/v1/leaves` â€“ Request leave  
- `DELETE /api/v1/leaves/:id` â€“ Cancel leave  

> **For full API documentation, check the backend folder.**

